      <scopecontent id="aspace_d4694b39ff9085133e6ac02f3a45fb3d">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The Insignia Films Lindbergh documentary collection consists of films and sound recordings created and used for a biography of Anne and Charles Lindbergh for the <title render="italic">
               <part>American Experience</part>
            </title> television program produced on public television.</p>  
